Registration Confirmation

Dear <%= @guardian_name %>,

Thank you for registering your child(ren) for California Kids Camp! We're excited to have them join us.

<% if @attendee_registration.paid? %>
PAYMENT RECEIPT
===============

Payment Date: <%= @attendee_registration.updated_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %>
Payment Type: <%= @attendee_registration.payment_type == "deposit" ? "Deposit" : "Full Payment" %>
Pricing Type: <%= @attendee_registration.pricing_type_display %>
Number of Attendees: <%= @attendee_registration.attendees.count %>
Total Amount: $<%= sprintf("%.2f", @attendee_registration.calculate_total_amount) %>
Amount Paid: $<%= sprintf("%.2f", @attendee_registration.amount_paid || 0) %>
<% if @attendee_registration.remaining_balance > 0 %>
Remaining Balance: $<%= sprintf("%.2f", @attendee_registration.remaining_balance) %>
<% end %>
Payment Status: <%= @attendee_registration.payment_status_display %>

<% end %>

REGISTERED ATTENDEES
====================
<% @attendee_registration.attendees.each do |attendee| %>
- <%= attendee.first_name %> <%= attendee.last_name %> - Age <%= attendee.age %>
<% end %>

If you have any questions or need to make changes to your registration, please don't hesitate to contact us.

We look forward to seeing you at camp!

Best regards,
California Kids Camp Team
